8 Subject: Education; University of Vermont; enrollment cap; housing
9 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to (1) limit the
10 enrollment of the University of Vermont and State Agricultural College when
11 the vacancy rate of the City of Burlington is below five percent; (2) require
12 University housing to meet municipal housing codes and rental housing health
13 and safety standards; and (3) establish the UVM Housing Task Force to
14 monitor compliance.
